list.abstract: grade，英文单词，作名词、动词，翻译为等级、分数、成绩、把…分等级、逐渐变化等意思。

yingyinNormal.en: I love the second grade. Really?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢二年级。真的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Phoebe, we're getting married, married, not sixth grade married.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是要“结婚”结婚，不是“六年级”的结婚。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah. Fifth grade. Sixth grade. Seventh grade. Eighth grade. Ninth grade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的哎，五年级时的身高，六年级时的身高，七年级时的身高，八年级时的身高，九年级时的身高。

yingyinNormal.en: Seventh grade middle school.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中学七年级。

yingyinNormal.en: Yup. everything since the eighth grade. The eighth grade? My last growth spurt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，从我八年级到现在所有的。八年级？我从那时起就不再长了。

yingyinNormal.en: No, Riley, you're not donezo. That's just one grade on one test.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，莱丽，你没完，只是一次考试的一次成绩而已。

yingyinNormal.en: Except for one thing. This is a one-week class for you, a grade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但还有一件事，这是你们一周的课程 ，全年级都是。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you doing? I'm afraid that's above your pay grade, honey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们在干什么？你还不够级别过问这事，宝贝。

yingyinNormal.en: Farkle, you're the biggest flirt in seventh grade. Well, thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 弗科，你是7年级最会调情的人了。谢谢夸奖。

yingyinNormal.en: Still playing cop, huh? Trust me, this is way above your pay grade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还在扮演警察的角色，是吗？相信我，这不是你这级别的人该知道的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I don't know. I've been wanting this since ninth grade typing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从九年级的打字课起就想要这一刻。

yingyinNormal.en: Honey, you just need to study more. You're gonna pick your grade up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，你只是需要多多学习，你的成绩会提上来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, so I spent seventh grade dotting my I's with little asses? Cool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也就是说我的七年级一直都用的小屁股作为点缀了是吧？酷啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I've been doing it since ninth grade. I've got pretty damn good at it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从九年级就开始这样了，我早驾轻就熟了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, guys, seventh grade student council elections are coming up. Yay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，同学们，七年级学生会选举就快要举行了。太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: That's nothing. In ninth grade, the girls put Rogaine in my hand lotion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不算什么，九年级的时候那些女生在我的护手霜里下洛盖尼。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. It's so much better than first grade when you don't know what's going on and definitely better than third grade. You know with all the politics and mind games.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它比一年级好多了，也比三年级好，你可以玩尔虞我诈的斗智游戏。

yingyinNormal.en: Ooh, seventh grade party. Yup, I didn't get invited to a whole lot of these.
yingyinNormal.zh: 呀，七年级派对呢，没错，我就从来没被邀请过参加这类活动。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, right, well yeah, I graduated fourth grade and realized I wasn't a pimp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 升上五年级之后，我发现我不是个男妓。

yingyinNormal.en: The Bay City Rollers for dancing. Wait, that was from my sixth grade wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三重奏跳舞时用湾市摇滚（七八十年代的合唱团），等一下，那是我的六年级婚礼。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我在七年级的时候，我参加了一个英语歌唱比赛。

examination_example.sentence: Forty students in Class One, <highlight>Grade</highlight> Nine are fond of reading novels written in English.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一年级、九年级的四十名学生喜欢读英文小说。

examination_example.sentence: I often faced situations like this during my <highlight>grade</highlight> school.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在我上小学期间，我经常面临这样的情况。

word_usage.usage:
“?读...年级”用"in ... grade"表达，“取得好成绩”用get good grades。
示例：Sam is in (the) second grade. 
萨姆读二年级。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指比赛的最终结果，或某一门考试的得分。
指学习或考试成绩，通常用字母而非数字表示。
尤指老师给学生的分数、成绩。
主要指运动、比赛中的得分，有时也指考试的分数。
